### Ant Task

aura command line as explained in the usage page should be able to suffcient in most of the cases. If there is a requirement to leverage more of 
aura the you can use ANT tasks as expained below. 

Many orgnisation have investment in automation scripts and using the tasks user can integrated aura in existing ANT automation scripts. 
